sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant F1 as Follower 1
    participant F2 as Follower 2
    participant C as Candidate
    participant L as Leader

    Note over F1,C: Followers' election timers expire (1500–2000 ms)

    F1->>C: RequestVote(term=T)
    F2->>C: RequestVote(term=T)
    C-->>F1: VoteGranted
    C-->>F2: VoteGranted

    Note over C,L: Candidate wins majority → becomes Leader (term=T)

    loop Every 750 ms (heartbeat)
        L->>F1: AppendEntries (heartbeat)
        L->>F2: AppendEntries (heartbeat)
        F1-->>L: AppendEntriesResponse(success)
        F2-->>L: AppendEntriesResponse(success)
    end

    Note over L: Leader maintains authority<br>until higher term observed
